52
00:03:44,720 --> 00:03:48,020
When the next Tribe Chief is confirmed

53
00:03:48,030 --> 00:03:50,760
or whoever makes outstanding contribution
to the tribe,

54
00:03:50,760 --> 00:03:53,690
