will be awarded to that person.

55
00:04:00,480 --> 00:04:02,510
<i>The same cliff,</i>

56
00:04:02,510 --> 00:04:05,920
<i>the same oppression by
the Tribe Elder last-named Tang.</i>

57
00:04:05,920 --> 00:04:07,680
<i>I’ve never expected that in my second life,</i>

58
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:11,220
<i>I still can’t escape from the same fate.</i>

59
00:04:11,230 --> 00:04:15,310
<i>But in this life,
I’ll take control of my own destiny.</i>

60
00:04:15,370 --> 00:04:18,010
Seventh Elder,
whoever leaves between the mountains loses.

61
00:04:18,010 --> 00:04:19,710
