He’s indeed a little freak.

74
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:12,730
After a decade, a new prodigy emerges.

75
00:05:12,730 --> 00:05:14,080
Watch out.

76
00:05:14,080 --> 00:05:16,110
Death God Domain.

77
00:05:19,280 --> 00:05:20,910
<i>Confronting with
a Grand Soul Land Master,</i>

78
00:05:20,910 --> 00:05:23,560
