79
00:05:41,500 --> 00:05:43,660
Third Soul Skill,

80
00:05:43,660 --> 00:05:46,080
Clear Burning Sun.

81
00:05:50,160 --> 00:05:53,840
<i>I can clearly feel that the power of
Hao Tian Hammer is soaring.</i>

82
00:05:53,840 --> 00:05:56,170
