91
00:07:17,960 --> 00:07:20,000
<i>First Soul Skill, Intertwine.</i>

92
00:07:25,930 --> 00:07:27,390
<i>Third Soul Skill,</i>

93
00:07:27,390 --> 00:07:29,100
<i>Constraint of Spider Web.</i>

94
00:07:29,770 --> 00:07:31,390
<i>Blue Silver Domain.</i>

95
00:07:33,630 --> 00:07:35,840
<i>The spiderweb not only can not restrain me,</i>

96
00:07:35,840 --> 00:07:37,660
<i>it’ll be hindered by the iron chain bridge as well.</i>

97
