Is it because of the gravity control?</i>

100
00:07:56,030 --> 00:07:57,260
Sixth Soul Skill,

101
00:07:57,260 --> 00:07:58,300
Martial Soul Clone.

102
00:07:58,300 --> 00:08:02,170
<i>Now any skill that Seventh Elder
performs through the Hao Tian Hammer</i>

103
00:08:02,170 --> 00:08:04,110
