104
00:08:04,110 --> 00:08:06,030
Fifth Soul Skill,

105
00:08:06,030 --> 00:08:07,720
Gravity Control.

106
00:08:17,950 --> 00:08:19,240
This is bad.

107
00:08:19,950 --> 00:08:21,550
Second Soul Skill,

108
00:08:21,550 --> 00:08:23,880
Hammer Soul Control.

109
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:30,320
<i>That’s fast.</i>

110
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:34,000
<i>Blue Silver Domain.</i>

111
00:08:37,740 --> 00:08:39,280
<i>Death God Domain.</i>

112
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:44,840
Not merely soul skills but also
the gap of actual combat experience.

113
00:08:44,840 --> 00:08:46,640
