114
00:08:46,640 --> 00:08:49,420
<i>He’s a good opponent worth fighting with.</i>

115
00:08:49,420 --> 00:08:50,400
<i>Ghostly Trace.</i>

116
00:09:12,910 --> 00:09:17,200
