118
00:09:24,640 --> 00:09:27,080
<i>Oppressed to such extent by my Hao Tian Hammer,</i>

119
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:32,170
<i>he’s still able to dodge briskly
without a trace of fatigue.</i>

120
00:09:32,170 --> 00:09:33,850
<i>After opening up the Eight Meridians,</i>

121
00:09:33,850 --> 00:09:36,400
<i>my body recovers faster than it used to.</i>

122
00:09:45,050 --> 00:09:49,000
<i>Seventh Brother has used more than 40% of his soul power,</i>

123
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:51,790
<i>is he eager to win?</i>

124
00:09:51,790 --> 00:09:56,800
<i>After all, Tang San has surprised us a lot.</i>

125
00:09:59,280 --> 00:10:01,900
<i>The seventh soul skill is
much more powerful.</i>

126
00:10:01,900 --> 00:10:06,280
<i>This means that Little San has to deal with
two Tool Soul Form.</i>

127
00:10:13,420 --> 00:10:15,260
<i>In this situation,</i>

128
00:10:15,260 --> 00:10:17,930
