142
00:11:58,310 --> 00:12:00,120
Tool Soul Form.

143
00:12:05,110 --> 00:12:07,020
<i>It’s a spontaneous defense
invoked by accident.</i>

144
00:12:07,020 --> 00:12:09,820
<i>Seventh Elder has exerted
all of his soul power.</i>

145
00:12:19,210 --> 00:12:22,060
