148
00:13:04,330 --> 00:13:06,970
Fifth Soul Skill, Impregnable Defense.

149
00:13:16,040 --> 00:13:18,450
<i>Lame trick.</i>

150
00:13:20,330 --> 00:13:21,980
Blue Silver Domain.

151
00:13:21,980 --> 00:13:25,660
<i>I’m frozen under this power...</i>

152
00:13:48,970 --> 00:13:50,470
Little San...

153
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:59,510
Uncle, I’m alright. No worries.

154
00:14:02,710 --> 00:14:08,280
<i>Brother Hao,
you’ve raised him into a little freak.</i>

155
00:14:12,790 --> 00:14:15,320
