the Eight Spider Bone.</i>

158
00:14:31,580 --> 00:14:33,980
<i>I’m only slightly injured.</i>

159
00:14:34,540 --> 00:14:36,550
Seventh Uncle lost out big this time.

160
00:14:36,550 --> 00:14:38,780
