161
00:14:38,780 --> 00:14:40,670
Stop his impulsiveness.

162
00:14:49,710 --> 00:14:53,320
Where’s that brat?
Has he been broken by me?

163
00:14:55,690 --> 00:14:57,820
How did he get up here?

164
00:14:57,820 --> 00:15:00,360
Did you save him, Tribe Chief?

165
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:02,090
