168
00:15:07,530 --> 00:15:09,390
Face it.

169
00:15:09,390 --> 00:15:11,370
We’ve witnessed it.

170
00:15:11,370 --> 00:15:13,560
If I’m not wrong,

171
00:15:13,560 --> 00:15:16,790
