172
00:15:16,790 --> 00:15:19,790
- He didn’t use it in the duel.
- But...

173
00:15:19,790 --> 00:15:25,150
Enough. You broke your promise in the duel.

174
00:15:25,150 --> 00:15:29,400
You’ve lost.

175
00:15:33,240 --> 00:15:36,680
<i>What’s going on?
My soul skill has been forcibly cut off.</i>

176
00:15:36,680 --> 00:15:40,220
<i>It’s due to the domain resulted from the
scattering of Blue Silver Tyrant Spear.</i>

177
00:15:40,220 --> 00:15:43,720
<i>No way.
I must get off from this deadlock.</i>

178
00:15:53,930 --> 00:15:57,720
A bet is a bet. Since I’ve lost,

179
00:15:57,720 --> 00:16:00,590
I’ll do as I promised him.

180
00:16:02,350 --> 00:16:07,290
Dismiss, everyone.
Return to your practice.

181
00:16:07,290 --> 00:16:08,750
Yes.

182
00:16:13,070 --> 00:16:14,940
Yue Hua,

183
00:16:14,940 --> 00:16:18,920
