185
00:16:21,080 --> 00:16:27,880
It’s not that we approve it,
but Tang San himself earned it.

186
00:16:27,880 --> 00:16:32,060
I have never seen
such an outstanding young man.

187
00:16:32,060 --> 00:16:35,560
I hope he won’t go off track in the future.

188
00:16:35,560 --> 00:16:38,460
Don’t make his father’s mistake.

189
00:16:40,950 --> 00:16:45,240
Tribe Elders, Hao Tian Tribe
has gone into hiding for years.

190
00:16:45,240 --> 00:16:48,360
