191
00:16:50,220 --> 00:16:54,360
Tribe Chief, do you mean...

192
00:16:54,360 --> 00:16:56,640
It has been 20 years.

193
00:16:56,650 --> 00:17:00,890
It’s time for Hao Tian Hammer
to reemerge in the soul masters’ world.

194
00:17:00,890 --> 00:17:04,839
You have repeatedly request me
to lift the ban, no?

195
00:17:04,839 --> 00:17:10,029
I think now it’s time.

196
00:17:10,030 --> 00:17:12,550
I don’t agree.

197
00:17:12,550 --> 00:17:14,730
I reckon,

198
00:17:14,730 --> 00:17:18,270
