to stay low for a while.

199
00:17:18,270 --> 00:17:19,630
Because of Little San?

200
00:17:19,630 --> 00:17:27,099
Yes. Hao Tian Tribe needs a leader
who can lead the tribe to forge ahead.

201
00:17:27,099 --> 00:17:31,390
We’ve grown old and so have you.

202
00:17:31,390 --> 00:17:35,100
But it’s a different case for him.

203
00:17:35,100 --> 00:17:37,590
He’s so talented.

204
00:17:37,590 --> 00:17:43,050
We must not neglect him
due to the reemergence of the tribe.

205
00:17:43,050 --> 00:17:46,490
He needs training and guidance.

206
00:17:46,490 --> 00:17:49,510
The tribe should stay put

207
00:17:49,510 --> 00:17:52,280
