Brother Hao?

209
00:17:56,360 --> 00:18:01,740
No, don’t you remember
the three requests I mentioned before?

210
00:18:01,740 --> 00:18:04,840
If he can accomplish all of them,

211
00:18:04,840 --> 00:18:09,560
